on.<br><br><br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uazathool.showPublicProfile?language=EN>azathool</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 961<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/1/02 12:09:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11675.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.azathool.com/IMAGES/moving-aza.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tstaff blues</span><hr size=1> I know someone who did camp one (he was 60th Epic/Fungi), but he wanted one more than anything else (btw, not me !).<br><br>He got it on something like his 257th Skelly WL. With one WL every ~45 mins, that took him about 200 hours of camping.<br><br>I can easily farm 300 pp straight (ie, raw) pp an hour in several zones, and more if I try hard. So in the same time, he could have farmed 60K cash and bought one.<br><br>You have to contend with actually getting the camp every day, keeping the camp, people who take a peep into WL room and train you, the inane /ooc and /shout'ing there, and it's also a pain to run to the DL spire to get anywhere. <p><br><br><hr><table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">  <tr>    <td width="60">      <p align="center"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=597"><img border="0" src="http://www.azathool.com/IMAGES/moving-aza.gif" alt="Azathool" width="60" height="60"></a></td>    <td width="100%" bgcolor="#CCCCCC">      <p align="center" style="line-height: 100%; text-indent: 0; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=597"><b><font face="Monotype Corsiva" size="3" color="#000000">Azathool</font></